        "LiquidInfrastructureNFT.thresholdErc20s/thresholdAmounts (arrays controlling Cosmos module behavior / withdrawal token list discovery)",
        "LiquidInfrastructureNFT ERC721 ownership/approvals (ownerOf(AccountId), getApproved(AccountId), isApprovedForAll) used as privilege state"
      ],
      "privilege_assets": [
        "LiquidInfrastructureERC20 Ownable.owner() authority: approveHolder/disapproveHolder/mint/mintAndDistribute/addManagedNFT/releaseManagedNFT/setDistributableERC20s and inherited transferOwnership/renounceOwnership",
